Provide a www interface to easily change UNIX / Samba passwords and watch Wifi connections.
See http://yeupou.wordpress.com/2012/12/23/setting-up-a-silentlow-energy-consumption-home-server-dhcpdnssmbupnp/

Requires: perl CGI, DBI, mysql-server.

To create the database:

mysql -e "CREATE DATABASE updatepasswords
mysql -e "CREATE TABLE requests (ip_address varchar(32) NOT NULL default '0', user_name text NOT NULL)" updatepasswords
mysql -e "CREATE USER 'www-data'@'locahost' IDENTIFIED BY 'TO_DEFINE'"
mysql -e "GRANT ALL ON updatepasswords.* TO 'www-data'@'localhost'"